      • getIndex

        public int getIndex()
        Gets the index of this FreeColSpecObjectType. The index imposes a total ordering consistent with equals on each class extending FreeColSpecObjectType, but this ordering is nothing but the order in which the objects of the respective class were defined. It is guaranteed to remain stable only for a particular revision of a particular specification. Kludge to make this public so that MapViewer can see it.
        Returns:
        The game object index.
